<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Welcome to Modo! Confirm Your Account</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f7f9fc; /* Light background */
      color: #333;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
    }
    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); /* Subtle shadow */
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #6a05ad; /* A vibrant, modern purple */
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #2c3e50; /* Darker text for headings */
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      color: #555;
    }
    .button-wrapper {
      margin-top: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .confirm-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #007bff; /* A standard blue for action */
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 15px 35px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 19px;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.2); /* Shadow for button */
    }
    .confirm-button:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
      transform: translateY(-1px); /* Slight lift on hover */
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f0f2f5;
      padding: 25px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #777;
      border-top: 1px solid #e0e2e5;
    }
    .footer p {
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="header">
      Welcome to Our Community!
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h1>Hello, {{name}}!</h1>
      <p>Thanks for joining Modo ðŸ˜Š  We're excited to have you.</p>
      <p>To finalize your account setup and unlock all the features, please click the button below to confirm your email address.</p>

      <div class="button-wrapper">
        <a href="{{url}}" class="confirm-button">Confirm My Account Now</a>
      </div>

      <p>This ensures the security of your account and helps us keep you updated.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>If you didn't create an account with us, please simply ignore this email.</p>
      <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} Modo. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>